node.text: For quite some time now tbh @phranqueigh

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Me one week week into September: WHERE THE FALL WEATHER?'.

node.text: My last serotonin molecules are fuelled solely by fall foliage @mybestiesays

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 05, 2021 tagging @lucifernetflix. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Me looking shocked after doing exactly the opposite of what my therapist told me to do and it turns out bad'.

node.text: Who would’ve thought?! Watch it all play out on @lucifernetflix launching September 10th! #NetflixPartner #LuciferFinalSeason

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 05, 2021. May be a meme of 1 person and text that says 'me thinking about taking another nap after just napping for five hours'.

node.text: Napping is a skill right? Right. @mybestiesays

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'When someone asks you "what's wrong?" but nothing's actually wrong, that's just how your face looks normally'.
Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'If a demon possessed me would be like ok, take it from here good luck'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'evan nicole brown @theevanarysays I think everybody deserves 6 months off of work to focus on the world crumbling around us maybe more'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Almost left the grocery store without buying a bag of spring mix to throw, unopened, into the garbage in two weeks.'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 02, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'Me on my way to tell my best friend something I'm not supposed to tell anybody @heavyvanilla'.
Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'It might be called social media but all I do is share memes and ignore people'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I don't even have a sense of humor anymore it's literally just sarcasm and general loathing for the majority of the human population.'.

node.text: Hate hate hate double hate LOATHE entirely @mybestiesays
